{"ID":"20220618223329-mim6o0w","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20220618223329-mim6o0w","title":"各类电影台词","type":"doc","updated":"20220621095428"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220618223330-bjk9ckv","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220618223330-bjk9ckv","updated":"20220618223330"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"心灵捕手"}]},{"ID":"20220620133642-mayyfzz","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220620133642-mayyfzz","updated":"20220621095428"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20220620133644-bdsxbx6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220620133644-bdsxbx6","updated":"20220621095428"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"Every day I come by your house, and I pick you up.We go out and have a few drinks and few laughs, and it's great.You know what the best part of my day is?It's for about ten seconds: from when I pull up to the curb and when I get to your door.'Cause I think maybe I'll get up there and I'll knock on the door and you won't be there.No \u0026quot;good-bye,\u0026quot; no \u0026quot;see ya later.\u0026quot; No nothing. You just left.I don't know much, but I know that."},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\n我每天到你家接你，我们出去喝酒笑闹，那很棒。但我一天中最棒的时刻只有十秒，从停车到你家门口，每次我敲门，都希望你不在了，不说再见，什么都没有，你就走了，我懂得不多，但我很清楚"}]}]},{"ID":"20220620133628-5gf3svd","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220620133628-5gf3svd","updated":"20220620133907"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"模仿游戏"}]},{"ID":"20220620133918-xv0v7z4","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220620133918-xv0v7z4","updated":"20220620133920"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20220620133920-o88f5c8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220620133920-o88f5c8","updated":"20220620133920"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4、有时候，正是那些无人看好的人能取得无人能及的成就。"}]},{"ID":"20220620133920-yd26lh1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220620133920-yd26lh1","updated":"20220620133920"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"sometimes it's the very people who no one imagines anything of who do the things no one can imagine."}]}]},{"ID":"20220620133944-6cvab8g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220620133944-6cvab8g"}}]}